    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This example boasts crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and maintains excellent lateral stability through a limited-slip differential. The chassis is well-sorted, having undergone a recent subframe reinforcement and VANOS system overhaul to ensure long-term durability. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a driven enthusiast car, the suspension geometry remains true and the powertrain delivers a linear torque curve all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. A reliable, high-performance icon ready for the apex.",
