    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 530i that perfectly balances executive elegance with athletic performance. The exterior is finished in a stunning Mineral White Metallic that retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Mocha Dakota leather and fine wood trim; the seats remain firm and supple, and the interior retains that signature premium scent. Every technological amenity, including the intuitive iDrive infotainment system, multi-zone climate control, and the crisp Harman Kardon surround sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been treated with the utmost care, boasting a comprehensive service record from authorized technicians. The turbocharged engine delivers smooth, responsive power, while the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride over any surface. It sits on original alloy wheels wrapped in high-quality tires with plenty of life left. This is a turn-key luxury sedan for the discerning driver who values a vehicle that has been loved and respected by its owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
