    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and the occasional road trip. It\u2019s well-loved, runs great, and is ready for its next owner to jump in and go! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels fantastic, this is the one for you. Let me know if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
