    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46-generation M3, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M-variable limited-slip differential for superior power delivery. Mechanical integrity is a priority here; the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The chassis retains its communicative nature with refreshed bushings and a revised cooling system to manage thermal loads during spirited driving. While the aesthetics show minor signs of use consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and suspension kinematics remain tight and responsive. A mechanically robust specimen ready for the apex.",
